creator: Rescue games dev RGD
descriptionHtml:
Shooting with puzzles! 💣💥 You've never seen anything like this before!
A modern game that will not leave anyone indifferent.
Who didn't Like to play pistols as a child and pretend to be a ninja?!
imagine yourself as a super agent or spy and complete missions of varying difficulty. We have come up with a huge number of levels with puzzles and different challenges where you need to save a person. You won't get bored
with the game, that's for sure!
: save the civilians, with the help of the main character, whose name is Bob, destroying all the enemies. Get 3 stars and you will become a master.

Use a pistol to save a person who is in trouble from the villain with one shot or use several bullets. Shooting on various moving platforms develops accuracy, solve puzzles with your friends and compete with them. Blowing up fuel barrels is so much fun!

At the moment, we have more than 100 missions and this is not the limit. We are developing even more challenges and puzzles for you. Shooting at enemies with a gun, what could be more interesting?!
Hit the bull's eye, develop speed, be accurate, take aim at the villain and save the person.

Rescue bullet is a game that will let you relax and enjoy a lot of levels where you can shoot at moving objects and enemies, break glass blocks and save innocent people. For each completed mission, you will receive a reward 💰.

Saving a person is your most important task.
Use all your accuracy and dexterity, and you will have to solve complex puzzles to complete each level. 🛡The protection of humanity now rests on your shoulders. Now your best friend is a gun🔫, let's see if you can complete a whole level with one shot. Complete all levels with three-star puzzles to unlock additional seasons and bonus items.
